Kubernetes v1.12 introduced RuntimeClass: you can have multiple runtimes per cluster!
https://kubernetes.io/blog/2018/10/10/kubernetes-v1.12-introducing-runtimeclass/

kata containers work with docker, cri-o and containerd
intel leading, solid and maturing

AWS firecracker
originating from crosvm, targets serverless/functions area
quickly moving and young project

gvisor
kernel in userspace concept from Google in Go
works standalone or with containerd
limited functionality; some applications may not work if the syscall is not implemented by gvisor

singularity
HPC/academic community focused container runtime by syslab
